    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/6228b5b8f7c08829490ea4f6b7223ad8.avif?t=1750151066\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/d38e1d2a53afed8b95b52f7145375666.webp?t=1750151066\" width=620 height=60 /></span>在《诸神之劫：自走棋》中，感受前所未有的诸神之战！你将招募来自不同神话的强大神明，通过升级和巧妙布阵，打造一支无敌的神明队伍。面对无尽宇宙中的恐怖，只有最强的决策者才能战到最后！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/1cabcb32c24576d3b8266823e2de704a.poster.avif?t=1750151066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/1cabcb32c24576d3b8266823e2de704a.webm?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/1cabcb32c24576d3b8266823e2de704a.mp4?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/9c0de618f351a2f343f9116f041b116c.webp?t=1750151066\" width=620 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次刷新卡牌，都可能为你的队伍带来新的神明，改变你的战略走向。你需要在增强现有力量和提升信仰等级之间找到平衡，稳步提升实力还是试图招募更强大的神明，一切都由你选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理安排神明的位置，利用自动战斗机制，体验每场战斗的快节奏与策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/adcc6cced7ce3b72aa9bd908cc3b57b9.poster.avif?t=1750151066\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/adcc6cced7ce3b72aa9bd908cc3b57b9.webm?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/adcc6cced7ce3b72aa9bd908cc3b57b9.mp4?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/4c9a45494954e3648093a196524ba080.webp?t=1750151066\" width=620 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中包含来自10种神话的165位神明和30种遗物，为你提供无限的组合可能。你还将不断解锁新的选择，创造独一无二的战斗组合。面对5个恐怖的Boss，每个Boss都有独特的挑战和环境效果，你需要灵活应对，制定策略，才能带领众神击败他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满变数的世界中，唯有最强的指挥者才能带领众神取得胜利。成为众神的领袖，征服所有的宇宙恐怖吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/75da6c0431c0266fcf9c2a9fc3b958af.poster.avif?t=1750151066\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/75da6c0431c0266fcf9c2a9fc3b958af.webm?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079080/extras/75da6c0431c0266fcf9c2a9fc3b958af.mp4?t=1750151066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
